overview.en: Green is a decentralized forest carbon sequestration stabilization currency developed and managed by Singapore Carbon Asset Management Corporation. Each Green unit represents 0.1 tons of real forest carbon sequestration contracts. 1 Green = 0.1t forest carbon sink contract. Green's value will continue to increase with the rapid development of global carbon markets.
overview.zh: Green是由新加坡碳资产管理公司开发并管理的去中心化森林碳汇稳定币，每个Green单位代表0.1吨真实的森林碳汇合约。1Green=0.1t森林碳汇合约。Green的价值将随全球各碳市场的快速发展而不断增值。
